reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great holiday party favors!
reviews.reviewText: This is a great set of holiday party favors! Kids love the stamps and notepads, and the rulers are a great idea. The pencils are nice - I just wish they came with sharpeners to make it easier for the kids to use them right away. The stickers are super cute. It's nice that cellophane gift bags were included. Overall, I'm pleased with this set.
